Fix malformed database_id in wrangler.toml.
Align worker allowedColumns and inspection form fields to match schema.sql
column names (inspection_id, inspection_date, process_id, parameter_id,
inspector_id, etc.) and expand table coverage to all 22 tables.
Remove duplicate schemas, sqlite dump, and unused jsx prototypes.
